4.2 Detailed Requirements
F1 — Verified Feed Layer
FR1.1 Connect to TxLINE via async SSE/websocket (asyncio + websockets).
FR1.2 Parse normalized JSON: fixture_id, match_time, score, odds, event_type, sequence, status_id, period.
FR1.3 For each critical input, store {sequence, timestamp, payload_hash, solana_validation_ref}.
FR1.4 Detect finalization via game_finalised, statusId=100, period=100.
FR1.5 Support fallback to recorded replay feed if live stream is empty.
Acceptance: Feed streams into system; every data point carries a verifiable reference; UI shows ✓ verified · seq #N.
F2 — Fair-Value Engine
FR2.1 Convert decimal odds → raw probability: 
