7. TECH STACK
Layer	Technology
Core engine	Python (asyncio + websockets)
Feed	TxLINE SSE (live) + recorded replay (demo safety)
On-chain	Solana devnet, Anchor framework
Verification	TypeScript (verify.ts)
Dashboard	Terminal UI + minimal web frontend
Explanation	LLM (explanation only, not decision)
Bonus package	@txline/sdk (open source)
