13. RISKS & MITIGATIONS
Risk	Impact	Mitigation
No live match during review	High	F8 deterministic replay
Live TxLINE stream empty	High	Recorded replay fallback
MM seen as "given idea" (novelty)	Medium	Emphasize event-aware self-hedging + receipts
Perceived as agent-controlled entry	Medium	Human-authored docs + commit history
Over-scoping kills MVP	High	Strict P0/P1/P2 discipline
Fake-looking metrics	Medium	All numbers from real replay output
